          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The instruction of the wise is like a life-giving fountain; those who accept it avoid the snares of death. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
